text:
The original application seems to be an abandonware (last release was more than 4 years ago, stale links at the website, no public repository, etc).

Our port has no maintainer. Seems that I should mark it BROKEN with option OYRANOS.

If you are in a deadly need of the port to work with oyranos you have some options:
. fix it;
. use old package/version (of oyranos);
. create a port of the needed version of oyranos.
